 *
 * Compatible with:
 *   - cPanel/WHM: /usr/local/cpanel/whostmgr/docroot/cgi/imh-php-extension/index.php
 *   - CWP:       /usr/local/cwpsrv/htdocs/resources/admin/modules/imh-php-extension.php
